values: You know...I haven't posted in my actual journal in I dunno...ever? Fuck that. I need to vent. I have had this journal since 2007. Fuck the fear of people finding it. Gonna change my photo then it is one. Fuck people. FUCK.

Dear Livejournal

Please don't throw out my journal...i dont write here but i do write in communities.

Love, Me

the end

So I peed on a stick this morning...

It came back negative, I am supposedly fetus free, but I remain unconvinced.

I am four days late, tired, ridiculously hungry alllll the time, nauseous ever morning for a week until around 11 and I finally feel better, emotional like you would not believe (I think I have cried more in the past week than I have in the past year) and the weirdest part...if i see, smell, touch or eat anything chocolate...I feel like vomiting. Me...not want chocolate.

So yeah...thats the cool events happening in my life.

Woo party

I am minorly amused because i have no actual journal posts....and yet i keep getting people that add me as a friend....so i figured i might as well give them something to read. Mind you, this is all you get for now, until i figure out something to write but...yeah...there u go...i posted        wooooooo party
